<title>
Fuel Pump Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A1706015">Fuel Pump Assembly Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Check fuel pump assembly for damage.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check fuel suction filter for contamination.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If contaminated, replace or clean the filter and check fuel tank inside for presence of dirt.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
